CPB (Cocoa Powder Bottle) License Agreement

1. Permitted Use

   The following uses are permitted:
   - Viewing, studying, and researching the source code
   - Personal use, educational use, and research use
   - Integration into your own projects (subject to Section 3)
   - Creation, sharing, and distribution of dictionaries
     (.cpbdict / .dict) without restriction

2. Prohibited Use

   The following uses are prohibited:
   - Use for any illegal purpose
   - Use for the purpose of data concealment, inspection evasion,
     or evidence destruction
   - Use for the purpose of infringing on the rights of others
   - Use as a component of weapons, surveillance systems,
     or systems involved in human rights violations

3. Integration and Redistribution

   If you integrate this software into your own project
   or redistribute it, the following conditions apply:
   - Include this license in full
   - Maintain attribution to the original author
   - If modified, clearly state that modifications were made
   - Pass these license terms to downstream users

4. Dictionary Freedom

   Creation, modification, sharing, distribution, and commercial
   use of dictionary files (.cpbdict / .dict) is unrestricted.
   Free circulation of dictionaries increases the value of CPB.

5. Author's Intent

   CPB is published as technology for compression, protection,
   and archival. The author does not condone misuse of this
   software. Users bear the responsibility to consider not only
   the technical utility but also the societal impact of their use.

6. Disclaimer

   This software is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind.
   The author assumes no liability for any damages arising from
   the use of this software. Any consequences of misuse are
   solely the responsibility of the user.

7. Governing Law

   This license is governed by the laws of Japan.


